.copy In the past TV choices were limited to broadcast networks.  Later, cable channels created hundreds of choices.  Noe, with the addition of streaming and on-demand services, choice is nearly unlimited -- creating a new problem: finding something to weatch.  Jinni partnered with ASTRO to develop an information design langauge and UX model that made their technology functionally friendly.

